title: VA World Pop Music - Home Again (Dutch Treat Sweetlist ^C058)
description:
32 songs straight from the heart. Funny when that happens, the artists and their songs (say) kind of invite themselves into the party. Until the list is full (30-33 tracks). I must admit, together they do quite nicely (without the Hits).

The sound may have suffered a bit from my choice of song; its still a very special playlist. On the edges of Pop, Folk, R&B, Electronic, Indie, lot of melodic sounding voices, some violins, some languages, just like Home Again. Each song with energy to give..... Enjoy,

PS Oh yes the cover. Seen that a lot. It does not hurt to think about that sometimes. Maybe you find Love. Like me when I saw a beam of light in the morning sky, announcing the sunrise at the end of the street.... Cover...
